{"type": "article", "id": 28986, "title": "自行车导航仪", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-01T06:49:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703124502B1TUzYI35LhGiaPN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>不少人会使用智能手机作为向导，然而对于骑自行车出行的人来说用手机导航反而会使人分心酿成事故。Blubel 是一款专门为自行车设计的导航仪，它的外观和传统的车铃无异，遇到紧急情况时也会尽职地发出清脆的铃声。Blubel 需要配合应用一起使用，设定好目的地之后 Blubel 会一路追踪你的位置，不断通过 LED 灯指示你骑行的方向。另一个非常贴心的功能在于它会记录用户响铃的位置上传到云端，一旦系统记录某处有密集的响铃记录，这个位置就会被标记为危险。如此一来，通过用户的共同努力，Blubel 会在下次规划路线时避开车况差的区域。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/372524908/blubel-the-cycling-navigator-powered-by-community\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 50 英镑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124500uH6LwPviRlY4UzmB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124501ZXlSIoAuwpeTVLtb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4904271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031245017Kg8lu0fQRYArvVM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55735294\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031245024WtYdV7bZB951iSc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57941176\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}